type.description: The type of the event, always `response.function_shell_command.delta`.

sequence_number.description: The sequence number of the event that was emitted.

output_index.description: The index of the output item that was updated.

command_index.description: The index of the shell command that was updated.

delta.description: The shell command delta that was appended.

obfuscation.description: An obfuscation string that was added to pad the event payload.

title: Response shell command delta event
description: A streaming event that indicated a shell command was incrementally updated.
